    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a showroom-quality depth and shine with no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, featuring premium materials that show virtually no signs of wear and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a powerful, smooth engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly. This is a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it was first delivered.",
