    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46). This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system recently recalibrated to factory specifications. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains surgically precise, benefiting from proactive subframe reinforcement and original suspension geometry. With flawless factory paint and an interior devoid of bolster wear or trim delamination, this mechanically superlative M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
